<body lang="id"><h2>PERHITUNGAN MANUAL METODE K-MEANS CLUSTERING<br>TOKO PARFUM R2DH</h2><h3>1. Data Mentah (Data Understanding)</h3><p>Data yang digunakan dalam penelitian ini adalah data penjualan parfum dari Toko Parfum R2DH yang berjumlah 200 data produk parfum dengan 5 kriteria penilaian, yaitu: Harga Parfum, Volume Penjualan, Frekuensi Pembelian, Jenis Aroma, Rating Pelanggan.</p><p class="center"><span class="bold">Tabel 1. Data Mentah Penjualan Parfum (10 Sampel Pertama)</span></p><table class="data-table"><thead><tr><th>No</th><th>Nama Produk</th><th>Harga Parfum</th><th>Volume Penjualan</th><th>Frekuensi Pembelian</th><th>Jenis Aroma</th><th>Rating Pelanggan</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1</td><td class="left">Black Orchid</td><td>Rp 360.000</td><td>2</td><td>15</td><td>Fresh</td><td>Tidak Dinilai</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td class="left">White Musk</td><td>Rp 150.000</td><td>8</td><td>15</td><td>Fresh</td><td>Bagus</td></tr><tr><td>3</td><td class="left">Blue Ocean</td><td>Rp 230.000</td><td>3</td><td>15</td><td>Woody</td><td>Bagus</td></tr><tr><td>4</td><td class="left">Midnight Rose</td><td>Rp 350.000</td><td>1</td><td>15</td><td>Fresh</td><td>Tidak Dinilai</td></tr><tr><td>5</td><td class="left">Vanilla Sky</td><td>Rp 160.000</td><td>5</td><td>15</td><td>Fresh</td><td>Tidak Dinilai</td></tr><tr><td>6</td><td class="left">Oud Royal</td><td>Rp 400.000</td><td>1</td><td>15</td><td>Woody</td><td>Bagus</td></tr><tr><td>7</td><td class="left">Amber Night</td><td>Rp 260.000</td><td>3</td><td>15</td><td>Woody</td><td>Tidak Dinilai</td></tr><tr><td>8</td><td class="left">Fresh Breeze</td><td>Rp 390.000</td><td>2</td><td>15</td><td>Woody</td><td>Bagus</td></tr><tr><td>9</td><td class="left">Golden Sand</td><td>Rp 350.000</td><td>3</td><td>15</td><td>Woody</td><td>Tidak Dinilai</td></tr><tr><td>10</td><td class="left">Dark Desire</td><td>Rp 270.000</td><td>4</td><td>15</td><td>Woody</td><td>Tidak Dinilai</td></tr><tr><td colspan="7" style="text-align:center; font-style:italic;">... dan seterusnya hingga data ke-200</td></tr></tbody></table><div class="page-break"></div><h3>2. Tahap Transformasi Data (Data Preparation)</h3><p>Sebelum data dapat diproses menggunakan algoritma K-Means, data mentah yang bersifat kategorikal maupun numerik perlu ditransformasi menjadi nilai bobot numerik. Berikut adalah aturan transformasi yang digunakan:</p><p class="center"><span class="bold">Tabel 2a. Aturan Transformasi Harga Parfum</span></p><table><tr><th>Rentang Harga</th><th>Bobot</th></tr><tr><td>≥ Rp 320.000</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td>Rp 270.000 – Rp 319.999</td><td>2</td></tr><tr><td>Rp 220.000 – Rp 269.999</td><td>3</td></tr><tr><td>Rp 190.000 – Rp 219.999</td><td>4</td></tr><tr><td>&lt; Rp 190.000</td><td>5</td></tr></table><p class="center"><span class="bold">Tabel 2b. Aturan Transformasi Volume Penjualan</span></p><table><tr><th>Volume</th><th>Bobot</th></tr><tr><td>9 – 10</td><td>5</td></tr><tr><td>7 – 8</td><td>4</td></tr><tr><td>5 – 6</td><td>3</td></tr><tr><td>3 – 4</td><td>2</td></tr><tr><td>1 – 2</td><td>1</td></tr></table><p class="center"><span class="bold">Tabel 2c. Aturan Transformasi Frekuensi Pembelian</span></p><table><tr><th>Frekuensi</th><th>Bobot</th></tr><tr><td>&gt; 10</td><td>2</td></tr><tr><td>5 – 10</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td>0 – 4</td><td>0</td></tr></table><p class="center"><span class="bold">Tabel 2d. Aturan Transformasi Jenis Aroma</span></p><table><tr><th>Jenis Aroma</th><th>Bobot</th></tr><tr><td>Oriental</td><td>2</td></tr><tr><td>Woody</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td>Fresh</td><td>0</td></tr></table><p class="center"><span class="bold">Tabel 2e. Aturan Transformasi Rating Pelanggan</span></p><table><tr><th>Rating</th><th>Bobot</th></tr><tr><td>Bagus / Ya</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td>Tidak Dinilai / Tidak</td><td>2</td></tr></table><div class="page-break"></div><h3>3. Hasil Transformasi Data</h3><p>Berdasarkan aturan transformasi di atas, berikut adalah hasil konversi seluruh data mentah menjadi nilai bobot:</p><p class="center"><span class="bold">Tabel 3. Data Setelah Transformasi (Seluruh 200 Data)</span></p><table class="data-table"><thead><tr><th>No</th><th>Nama Produk</th><th>Harga</th><th>Volume</th><th>Frekuensi</th><th>Aroma</th><th>Rating</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1</td><td class="left">Black Orchid</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>2</td><td>0</td><td>2</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td class="left">White Musk</td><td>5</td><td>4</td><td>2</td><td>0</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td>3</td><td class="left">Blue Ocean</td><td>3</td><td>2</td><td>2</td><td>1</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td>4</td><td class="left">Midnight Rose</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>2</td><td>0</td><td>2</td></tr><tr><td>5</td><td class="left">Vanilla Sky</td><td>5</td><td>3</td><td>2</td><td>0</td><td>2</td></tr><tr><td>6</td><td class="left">Oud Royal</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>2</td><td>1</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td>7</td><td class="left">Amber Night</td><td>3</td><td>2</td><td>2</td><td>1</td><td>2</td></tr><tr><td>8</td><td class="left">Fresh Breeze</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>2</td><td>1</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td>9</td><td class="left">Golden Sand</td><td>1</td><td>2</td><td>2</td><td>1</td><td>2</td></tr><tr><td>10</td><td class="left">Dark Desire</td><td>2</td><td>2</td><td>2</td><td>1</td><td>2</td></tr><tr><td>11</td><td class="left">Aqua Marine</td><td>3</td><td>2</td><td>2</td><td>0</td><td>2</td></tr><tr><td>12</td><td class="left">Sweet Blossom</td><td>1</td><td>3</td><td>2</td><td>1</td><td>2</td></tr><tr><td>13</td><td class="left">Velvet Oud</td><td>4</td><td>1</td><td>2</td><td>1</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td>14</td><td class="left">Citrus Bloom</td><td>4</td><td>3</td><td>2</td><td>1</td><td>2</td></tr><tr><td>15</td><td class="left">Ocean Mist</td><td>2</td><td>2</td><td>2</td><td>1</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td>16</td><td class="left">Floral Dream</td><td>4</td><td>2</td><td>2</td><td>1</td><td>2</td></tr><tr><td>17</td><td class="left">Mystic Wood</td><td>2</td><td>3</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>