>0</td><td>2</td></tr><tr><td>191</td><td class="left">Sweet Harmony</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td>192</td><td class="left">Ocean Calm</td><td>3</td><td>2</td><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td>193</td><td class="left">White Vanilla</td><td>2</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td>194</td><td class="left">Deep Forest Oud</td><td>1</td><td>4</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>2</td></tr><tr><td>195</td><td class="left">Fresh Blooming</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>2</td></tr><tr><td>196</td><td class="left">Soft Cotton</td><td>2</td><td>2</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td>197</td><td class="left">Royal Spirit</td><td>1</td><td>3</td><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td>198</td><td class="left">Sweet Night</td><td>5</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td>199</td><td class="left">Cool White</td><td>5</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td>200</td><td class="left">Elegant Ocean</td><td>5</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>1</td></tr></tbody></table><div class="page-break"></div><h3>4. Penentuan Centroid Awal</h3><p>Centroid awal ditentukan dari data produk yang telah dipilih sebagai acuan titik pusat cluster. Berikut centroid awal yang digunakan:</p><p class="center"><span class="bold">Tabel 4. Centroid Awal</span></p><table><thead><tr><th>Cluster</th><th>Nama Cluster</th><th>Produk Acuan</th><th>Harga</th><th>Volume</th><th>Frekuensi</th><th>Aroma</th><th>Rating</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class="bold">C1</td><td>Best Seller</td><td class="left">Fresh Wave</td><td>2</td><td>5</td><td>2</td><td>0</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td class="bold">C2</td><td>Low Demand</td><td class="left">Sweet Lily</td><td>4</td><td>1</td><td>2</td><td>1</td><td>1</td></tr></tbody></table><p class="no-indent" style="margin-left:36pt;"><span class="bold">C1 (Best Seller) — Fresh Wave:</span></p><ul><li>Harga: Rp 280.000 → Bobot 2</li><li>Volume Penjualan: 9 → Bobot 5</li><li>Frekuensi Pembelian: 15 → Bobot 2</li><li>Jenis Aroma: Fresh → Bobot 0</li><li>Rating Pelanggan: Bagus → Bobot 1</li></ul><p class="no-indent" style="margin-left:36pt;"><span class="bold">C2 (Low Demand) — Sweet Lily:</span></p><ul><li>Harga: Rp 190.000 → Bobot 4</li><li>Volume Penjualan: 1 → Bobot 1</li><li>Frekuensi Pembelian: 15 → Bobot 2</li><li>Jenis Aroma: Woody → Bobot 1</li><li>Rating Pelanggan: Bagus → Bobot 1</li></ul><div class="page-break"></div><h3>5. Rumus Euclidean Distance</h3><p>Perhitungan jarak antara setiap data dengan centroid menggunakan rumus Euclidean Distance:</p><p class="formula"><i>d(x, c) = √( (x₁ - c₁)² + (x₂ - c₂)² + (x₃ - c₃)² + (x₄ - c₄)² + (x₅ - c₅)² )</i></p><p class="no-indent">Dimana:</p><ul><li>x₁ = Bobot Harga, x₂ = Bobot Volume, x₃ = Bobot Frekuensi, x₄ = Bobot Aroma, x₅ = Bobot Rating</li><li>c₁...c₅ = Nilai centroid yang bersesuaian</li></ul><h3>5.1. Contoh Perhitungan Manual Iterasi Ke-1</h3><p class="no-indent">Centroid saat ini:</p><ul><li>C1 = [2, 5, 2, 0, 1]</li><li>C2 = [4, 1, 2, 1, 1]</li></ul><p class="no-indent" style="margin-left:18pt;"><span class="bold">Produk 1: Black Orchid [1, 1, 2, 0, 2]</span></p><p class="formula">d(Black Orchid, C1) = √( (1 - 2)² + (1 - 5)² + (2 - 2)² + (0 - 0)² + (2 - 1)² )</p><p class="formula">= √( 1 + 16 + 0 + 0 + 1 ) = √18 = <span class="bold">4.2426</span></p><p class="formula">d(Black Orchid, C2) = √( (1 - 4)² + (1 - 1)² + (2 - 2)² + (0 - 1)² + (2 - 1)² )</p><p class="formula">= √( 9 + 0 + 0 + 1 + 1 ) = √11 = <span class="bold">3.3166</span></p><p class="formula">Jarak minimum = <span class="bold">3.3166</span> → Masuk <span class="bold">C2</span></p><br><p class="no-indent" style="margin-left:18pt;"><span class="bold">Produk 2: White Musk [5, 4, 2, 0, 1]</span></p><p class="formula">d(White Musk, C1) = √( (5 - 2)² + (4 - 5)² + (2 - 2)² + (0 - 0)² + (1 - 1)² )</p><p class="formula">= √( 9 + 1 + 0 + 0 + 0 ) = √10 = <span class="bold">3.1623</span></p><p class="formula">d(White Musk, C2) = √( (5 - 4)² + (4 - 1)² + (2 - 2)² + (0 - 1)² + (1 - 1)² )</p><p class="formula">= √( 1 + 9 + 0 + 1 + 0 ) = √11 = <span class="bold">3.3166</span></p><p class="formula">Jarak minimum = <span class="bold">3.1623</span> → Masuk <span class="bold">C1</span></p><br><p class="no-indent" style="margin-left:18pt;"><span class="bold">Produk 3: Blue Ocean [3, 2, 2, 1, 1]</span></p><p class="formula">d(Blue Ocean, C1) = √( (3 - 2)² + (2 - 5)² + (2 - 2)² + (1 - 0)² + (1 - 1)² )</p><p class="formula">= √( 1 + 9 + 0 + 1 + 0 ) = √11 = <span class="bold">3.3166</span></p><p class="formula">d(Blue Ocean, C2) = √( (3 - 4)² + (2 - 1)² + (2 - 2)² + (1 - 1)² + (1 - 1)² )</p><p class="formula">= √( 1 + 1 + 0 + 0 + 0 ) = √2 = <span class="bold">1.4142</span></p><p class="formula">Jarak minimum = <span class="bold">1.4142</span> → Masuk <span class="bold">C2</span></p><br><p class="no-indent" style="margin-left:18pt;"><span class="bold">Produk 4: Midnight Rose [1, 1, 2, 0, 2]</span></p><p class="formula">d(Midnight Rose, C1) = √( (1 - 2)² + (1 - 5)² + (2 - 2)² + (0 - 0)² + (2 - 1)² )</p><p class="formula">= √( 1 + 16 + 0 + 0 + 1 ) = √18 = <span class="bold">4.2426</span></p><p class="formula">d(Midnight Rose, C2) = √( (1 - 4)² + (1 - 1)² + (2 - 2)² + (0 - 1)² + (2 - 1)² )</p><p class="formula">= √( 9 + 0 + 0 + 1 + 1 ) = √11 = <span class="bold">3.3166</span></p><p class="formula">Jarak minimum = <span class="bold">3.3166</span> → Masuk <span class="bold">C2</span></p><br><p class="no-indent" style="margin-left:18pt;"><span class="bold">Produk 5: Vanilla Sky [5, 3, 2, 0, 2]</span></p><p class="formula">d(Vanilla Sky, C1) = √( (5 - 2)² + (3 - 5)² + (2 - 2)² + (0 - 0)² + (2 - 1)² )</p><p class="formula">= √( 9 + 4 + 0 + 0 + 1 ) = √14 = <span class="bold">3.7417</span></p><p class="formula">d(Vanilla Sky, C2) = √( (5 - 4)² + (3 - 1)² + (2 - 2)² + (0 - 1)² + (2 - 1)² )</p><p class="formula">= √( 1 + 4 + 0 + 1 + 1 ) = √7 = <span class="bold">2.6458</span></p><p class="formula">Jarak minimum = <span class="bold">2.6458</span> → Masuk <span class="bold">C2</span></p><br><p>Dengan menggunakan rumus yang sama, perhitungan dilakukan untuk seluruh 200 data produk parfum.</p><div class="page-break"></div><h3>6.1. Iterasi Ke-1</h3><p class="center"><span class="bold">Tabel Centroid Iterasi Ke-1</span></p><table><tr><th>Cluster</th><th>Harga</th><th>Volume</th><th>Frekuensi</th><th>Aroma</th><th>Rating</th></tr><tr><td class="bold">C1</td><td>2</td><td>5</td><td>2</td><td>0</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td class="bold">C2</td><td>4</td><td>1</td><td>2</td><td>1</td><td>1</td></tr></table><p class="center"><span class="bold">Tabel Hasil Perhitungan Euclidean Distance Iterasi Ke-1</span></p><table class="data-table"><thead><tr><th>No</th><th>Nama Produk</th><th>Jarak ke C1</th><th>Jarak ke C2</th><th>Jarak Min</th><th>Cluster</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1</td><td class="left">Black Orchid</td><td>4.2426</td><td class="bold">3.3166</td><td class="bold">3.3166</td><td class="bold">C2</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td class="left">White Musk</td><td class="bold">3.1623</td><td>3.3166</td><td class="bold">3.1623</td><td class="bold">C1</td></tr><tr><td>3</td><td class="left">Blue Ocean</td><td>3.3166</td><td class="bold">1.4142</td><td class="bold">1.4142</td><td class="bold">C2</td></tr><tr><td>4</td><td class="left">Midnight Rose</td><td>4.2426</td><td class="bold">3.3166</td><td class="bold">3.3166</td><td class="bold">C2</td></tr><tr><td>5</td><td class="left">Vanilla Sky</td><td>3.7417</td><td class="bold">2.6458</td><td class="bold">2.6458</td><td class="bold">C2</td></tr><tr><td>6</td><td class="left">Oud Royal</td><td>4.2426</td><td class="bold">3.0000</td><td class="bold">3.0000</td><td class="bold">C2</td></tr><tr><td>7</td><td class="left">Amber Night</td><td>3.4641</td><td class="bold">1.7321</td><td class="bold">1.7321</td><td class="bold">C2</td></tr><tr><td>8</td><td class="left">Fresh Breeze</td><td>4.2426</td><td class="bold">3.0000</td><td class