3</td><td class="bold">C2</td></tr></tbody></table><div class="page-break"></div><h3>7. Cek Konvergensi</h3><p>Pada Iterasi Ke-6, posisi centroid tidak mengalami perubahan dibandingkan iterasi sebelumnya. Oleh karena itu, algoritma telah <span class="bold">KONVERGEN</span> dan proses perhitungan dihentikan.</p><p class="center"><span class="bold">Perbandingan Centroid</span></p><table><tr><th>Cluster</th><th>Centroid Iterasi 5</th><th>Centroid Iterasi 6</th><th>Status</th></tr><tr><td class="bold">C1</td><td>[1.4915, 2.4407, 1.1441, 0.7797, 1.5339]</td><td>[1.5122, 2.3821, 1.1382, 0.7724, 1.5447]</td><td>Sama</td></tr><tr><td class="bold">C2</td><td>[3.5244, 1.9146, 1.2073, 0.7805, 1.5976]</td><td>[3.6234, 1.974, 1.2208, 0.7922, 1.5844]</td><td>Sama</td></tr></table><div class="page-break"></div><h3>8. Kesimpulan Evaluasi K-Means</h3><p>Berdasarkan hasil perhitungan algoritma K-Means Clustering yang telah dilakukan sebanyak 6 iterasi hingga konvergen, diperoleh pengelompokan sebagai berikut:</p><p class="center"><span class="bold">Tabel Kesimpulan Pengelompokan</span></p><table><tr><th>Cluster</th><th>Nama Cluster</th><th>Jumlah Produk</th></tr><tr><td class="bold">C1</td><td>Best Seller</td><td>123 produk</td></tr><tr><td class="bold">C2</td><td>Low Demand</td><td>77 produk</td></tr></table><p class="center"><span class="bold">Anggota Cluster C1 (Best Seller)</span></p><table class="data-table"><thead><tr><th>No</th><th>Nama Produk</th><th>Jarak Minimum</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1</td><td class="left">Black Orchid</td><td>1.9285</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td class="left">Midnight Rose</td><td>1.9285</td></tr><tr><td>3</td><td class="left">Oud Royal</td><td>1.8066</td></tr><tr><td>4</td><td class="left">Fresh Breeze</td><td>1.8066</td></tr><tr><td>5</td><td class="left">Golden Sand</td><td>1.1875</td></tr><tr><td>6</td><td class="left">Dark Desire</td><td>1.1772</td></tr><tr><td>7</td><td class="left">Sweet Blossom</td><td>1.2829</td></tr><tr><td>8</td><td class=